First Create a Node App
Then install Nodemon
Then set npm run dev
Then create src folder
Create 6 folders,
Controllers
DB
Utils
Routes
Models
Middlewares
3 Files,
index
app
constants
Set Up Environmental variables.
in DB create index.js and write code to connect to Data Base
Then in app.js Write the code to create Express app
Then integrate both on Index.js

Write utilities in Utils
ApiResponse
ApiError
AsyncHandler

Then Create MODELS

Then create a utility cloudinary.js
go to website and copy and configure 
The create a function to upload to cloudinary

